name: The End of the War
debriefing: The last level in the game is passed! You won! ~~But... Look around - behind you are not just the interesting levels but also are piles of dead tank bodies, their broken-hearted families, starving children. Do you have at least a little of heart for them, huh? ~~Imagine, how much we have destroyed for the course of the game, how many lives we have terminated! ~~Well, what can we do now - the time is gone, and we can't bring it back... It's the bitterness of the victory. ~~And it is to be played over. How about another round? Or, if you thirst for fresh blood, you can download the new levels from the online menu!
briefing: It will come, but not right off, certainly. You owe the farewell battle!
